formData.text: Hello and welcome to Duck Debugging. What seems to be the problem?
variations: Duck debuggers here to assist! How can we help?
I'm a duck. You can talk to me. What's wrong?

formData.text: That sounds tough. You can figure it out.
variations: I'm sure you'll figure it out. Maybe I can help.
Ugh, I hate that. I have faith in you.

formData.text: What have you tried so far?
Sorry that hasn't helped. Is there something you're sure definitely couldn't be the cause?
And you're totally sure it's not that?
